Scott Sheffield, Pioneer Natural Resources
CEO
1012



CEO, July 3
 7:30 p.m.
 KERA TV
Scott Sheffield shares how Pioneer Natural Resources is positioned to ride the roller coaster oil and gas industry. Sheffield addresses environmental concerns associated with fracking and tells how advances in technology have led to efficiencies in drilling.
Watch the episode:





